title: THE DUMBEST GW IDEA IN A LONG TIME
description:
Game Workshop is putting their new Battle Forge army building app for Warhammer 40,000 behind a paywall - and they're doing it in the worst way possible.

Vince Venturella and I made another game! Check out MAJESTIC13 at http://www.majestic13game.com

I'm now a partner on Twitch! I paint minis every Friday morning and Monday night, and sometimes take paint breaks (play video games poorly). Follow me: http://www.twitch.tv/tabletopminions

Official Tabletop Minions t-shirts: http://bit.ly/merchbunker
